headline: Is Now the Time to Reassess UnitedHealth After a 35.9% Drop in 2025?
summary: Thinking about whether UnitedHealth Group is a bargain or just another blue-chip to watch? You are not alone, as many investors are asking if now is the right time to take a closer look at its valuation. The stock has seen notable moves recently, dropping 0.9% over the past week and falling 35.9% year-to-date, with its one-year return sitting at 45.4% lower. Recent headlines have focused on changing regulatory environments and sector-wide shifts in healthcare policy. Both of these factors...
